 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EFlit is a micro-blogging alternative where users are anonymous, have an equal voice, and promotes conversation.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ETwitter has fifty to eighty-million users, less than one percent of those users have more than one thousand followers. Imagine a mobile micro-blogging platform that gives the other ninety-nine percent of Twitter users a voice they don\u00e2\u20ac\u2122t currently have. Flit is that mobile micro-blogging platform where content is valued over followers, and conversation is valued over updates. There are three features that set Flit apart from its competitors: anonymity, conversation and every member of the community has a chance to be heard.\u003C/p\u003E",
